data.description: Welcome home to this stunning move in ready home! The large living space is beautifully designed with a split layout. This home was built in 2019. The modern home boasts a gorgeous, well - equipped kitchen that will inspire your inner chef. The architecture of this home is simply perfect, featuring eye catching stucco and rock overlay. New Exterior paint. The charming design features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The primary bathroom shower is what spa dreams are made of. This property offers a convenient shed with a roll-up door, perfect for storing, and or workshop space. Whether you're relaxing tastefully designed interiors or enjoying the tranquility of the outdoor space, this home truly offers perfect balance. Come see this gem today
